  "response": "While I don't have access to specific emails, I can suggest some effective email subject lines commonly used by e-commerce platforms like Snapdeal, Flipkart, and Amazon that typically catch attention. Here are a few examples:\n\n1. **Limited Time Offer: Get 50% Off Your Favorite Brands!**\n2. **Flash Sale Alert: Prices Slashed for 24 Hours Only!**\n3. **Your Wishlist Just Got Cheaper \u2013 Check Out the Deals!**\n4. **Unlock Exclusive Deals Just for You \u2013 Shop Now!**\n5. **Ready for a Shopping Spree? Discover Our New Arrivals!**\n6. **Don't Miss Out: Last Chance for Up to 70% Off!**\n7. **Surprise Inside: Unwrap Huge Savings This Weekend!**\n8. **Flash Deal: Your Favorite Items at Unbeatable Prices!**\n9. **It's Here: The Sale You\u2019ve Been Waiting For!**\n10. **Thank You for Shopping with Us \u2013 Here\u2019s a Special Gift!**\n\nThese subject lines often create a sense of urgency, exclusivity, or personalization, which can increase open rates and engagement.",
